---sequence Diagram-Driver Posts a ride-----
Actor: Driver 
Participant: MobileApp,RideController,RideService, RideRepository

-Driver>>MobileAPP: open post Ride form
-MobileApp>>Driver; Display form(origin , destination , time , seats, price)
Driver>>MobileApp: submit Ride details 
MobileAPP >> RideController; createRide(rideData, driverId)
RideController>>RideService ; createRide(ridedata, driverID)
RideService>>RideService: validateRideData(rideData)

DATA valid
rideService>>rideRepository; save(new ride)
rideRepository>>rideService; ride with rideID
rideService>>rideController MobileAPP; 'show ride posted successfully'

else data invalid;; 
rideService>>rideController: validationError
rideController>>MobileAPP: validation errors
